libD4000 is a share library providing a low-level interface to the TI/DLi Discovery D4000 
DMD Development kit.  In order to function correctly, the library requires the following
additional components:

- libusb0.1 : a library for communicating with usb devices in user space
- multiload or fxload : a tools for programming Cypress FX2 USB chips
- ezusb_a3load.hex, D4000_usb.hex & D4000_usb.bin : D4000 firmware files

